# dictionaryRepresentation()

**Instance Method**

Returns a dictionary representation of the map table.

## Declaration

```swift
func dictionaryRepresentation() -> [AnyHashable : ObjectType]
```

## Return Value

A dictionary representation of the map table.

## Discussion

The map table’s values and keys must conform to all the requirements specified in [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSMutableDictionary/setObject(_:forKey:)] in [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSMutableDictionary].
